[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ここが終点みたいね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00866",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "うわ、なんか、そ、ソー……なんだっけ、\n神秘的みたいな、でもちょっと怖いような",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00867",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "荘厳な雰囲気？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00868",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "それ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_037_00869",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "九偉人を崇拝する人々にとっての聖地だからな……\n周りにあるのは捧げものか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_037_00870",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そんな、お祈りとかするほどのもんじゃないわよ。\n九偉人なんてさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00871",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ヴァレリアを見てると、九偉人だって\n普通の人たちと変わんないもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00872",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "でしょ？　私だってそのつもりなのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00873",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "実際、九偉人が人間離れした強さを持ってるのも\n確かだからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00874",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "人は自分の持ってないものに憧れ、羨み、恐れる……\n少なくともここの人たちは、九偉人に救いを見たんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00875",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……やっぱり実感が湧かないのは、\n私の記憶が戻らないせいなのかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00876",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ねえ、あの真ん中にある、他より高い所！\nあそこにあるのって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00877",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "「九偉人図」！\n最後の１枚だ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00878",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "こういうとき、冒険譚ならそれを阻む\n凶悪な魔物が出てくるものだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00879",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "大丈夫みたいね。さっきのヤツが最後だったみたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00880",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ま、用心するに越したことはないし、\nそーっと、そーっと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00881",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "よし……！\n揃った！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00882",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "と、ここで洞窟全体が鳴動、\n落盤で出口が塞がれる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00883",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "え、ええっ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00884",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "……というのも、お話の中だけね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00885",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ビビッたぁ……\n王女を驚かせようなんて、あなた肝が据わってるね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00886",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "お母さん、ほんと程々にね……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00887",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……よし！　とにもかくにも手に入れた「九偉人図」。\n全部まとめて確認してみましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00888",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]